<hr><br>

<details><summary><span style="display: inline-block ; height: 30px ; width: 40px ; background: transparent url(&quot;https://play.pokemonshowdown.com/sprites/pokemonicons-sheet.png?v16&quot;) no-repeat scroll -360px -2580px"></span>When I edit my trainer card or host box, does the gallery get updated automatically?</summary>
<p>No. Updates are usually done manually by the gallerist when she spots a new trainer card or host box displayed in the room. In addition, the gallerist refrains from updating the same trainer card or host box twice within a short period of time in order to not overwork herself.</p></details>

<br><details><summary><span style="display: inline-block ; height: 30px ; width: 40px ; background: transparent url(&quot;https://play.pokemonshowdown.com/sprites/pokemonicons-sheet.png?v16&quot;) no-repeat scroll -360px -2580px"></span>How can I help updating the gallery?</summary>
<p>Fill in <a style="text-decoration:none; color: silver" href="https://forms.gle/j9WSwL7XLsSq7iM89">the exhibit submission form</a>. You are free to submit yours and other users' trainer cards and host boxes.</p></details>

<br><details><summary><span style="display: inline-block ; height: 30px ; width: 40px ; background: transparent url(&quot;https://play.pokemonshowdown.com/sprites/pokemonicons-sheet.png?v16&quot;) no-repeat scroll -360px -2580px"></span>Any future plans on improving the gallery?</summary>
<p>In order of importance:
<ol>
<li>Fixing the host box buttons</li>
<li>Implementing light theme<li>
</ol>
<br>PS: There is currently no plan to document scripted boxes and vote boxes.</p></details>

<br><details><summary><span style="display: inline-block ; height: 30px ; width: 40px ; background: transparent url(&quot;https://play.pokemonshowdown.com/sprites/pokemonicons-sheet.png?v16&quot;) no-repeat scroll -360px -2580px"></span>Is there a condensed version of the gallery's link?</summary>
